summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing the City Engineer to incur an indebtedness against the General Fund of The City of Seattle, in the sum of One Thousand One Hundred Six and 25/100 Dollars ($1106.25) for the purpose of completing the improvement of Thirty-first Avenue South et al., by grading the same, as authorized by Ordinance No. 19786, creating Local Improvement District No. 1916.
